  <summary date="2021-07-14T17:49:29Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Affordable Housing Redevelopment Act 

This bill reauthorizes the Neighborhood Stabilization Program for FY2021 to provide grants to states, local governments, and nonprofit entities for the conversion of blighted, abandoned, or foreclosed property into affordable housing for low-income families.</summary>
